song.title: Jackdance - Chug Mix
song.info:
This is not going to win any awards but I wanted to include it for posterity..
A previously unreleased Amiga remix from 2006 which I tried to retain the understated simplicity of the original. Jackdance was one of the earliest Amiga modules released and part of the infamous ST-01 collection composed by the Soundtracker legend himself, Karsten Obarski.
